{"sgc":false,"sfy":false,"qfy":false,"transUser":{"id":77539750,"status":99,"demand":1,"userid":5079841319,"nickname":"怀念加菲猫","uptime":1753408241268},"lyricUser":{"id":77539668,"status":99,"demand":0,"userid":382744871,"nickname":"已过期i","uptime":1753404297071},"lrc":{"version":4,"lyric":"{\"t\":0,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作词: \"},{\"tx\":\"SLANDER\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Dylan Matthew\"}]}\n{\"t\":1000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"Dylan Matthew\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Scott Land\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Derek Andersen\"}]}\n{\"t\":2000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"制作人: \"},{\"tx\":\"SLANDER\"}]}\n[00:14.160] Don't go tonight\n[00:18.850] Stay here one more time\n[00:22.190] Remind me what it's like\n[00:27.020] And let's fall in love one more time\n[00:34.370] I need you now by my side\n[00:41.170] It tears me up when you turn me down\n[00:48.050] I'm begging please, just stick around\n[00:55.760] I'm sorry, don't leave me, I want you here with me\n[01:02.600] I know that your love is gone\n[01:09.470] I can't breathe, I'm so weak, I know this isn't easy\n[01:16.330] Don't tell me that your love is gone\n[01:20.910] That your love is gone\n[01:24.404]\n[01:29.970] Don't tell me that your love is gone\n[01:34.750] That your love is gone\n[01:39.126]\n[01:50.420] I'm sorry, don't leave me, I want you here with me\n[01:57.200] I know that your love is gone\n[02:04.250] I can't breathe, I'm so weak, I know this isn't easy\n[02:14.610] Don't tell me that your love is gone\n[02:19.280] That your love is gone\n[02:26.120] That your love is gone, hmm\n[02:35.160] I can't breathe, I'm so weak, I know this isn't easy\n[02:42.690] Don't tell me that your love is gone\n[02:48.690] That your love is gone\n"},"klyric":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"tlyric":{"version":5,"lyric":"[by:怀念加菲猫]\n[00:14.160]今夜请别离去\n[00:18.850]再陪我片刻光阴\n[00:22.190]让我重温昔日情景\n[00:27.020]让我们再坠入爱河一次\n[00:34.370]此刻我需你依偎身旁\n[00:41.170]你的拒绝令我心如刀绞\n[00:48.050]我恳求你 请留在我身边\n[00:55.760]我深感愧疚 请不要离开我 我渴望你在此相伴\n[01:02.600]我深知 你